{"tid":179502,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎講下因為成長而改變嘅睇法","createTime":"2017-03-30T09:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T11:59:35.000Z","uid":96129,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c24ffcec605b938a6637fd6c5a9aad66a2527bf6","tid":179502,"uid":96129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T09:54:05.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講下長大後因為身邊嘅經歷而改變細個好理所當然嘅睇法<br />\n<br />\n我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細細個當老師係一種神聖不可侵犯嘅人，覺得佢地一定唔講粗口，生活健康，佢地講嘅野一定岩。遇到啲變態老師都會覺得好mindfucked 唔願意相信老師竟然可以咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。結果大個發現完全唔係呢回事，開始明老師都係人有佢情緒同私生活，又見過唔少讀教育嘅都好自私而且是非不分，而好果啲真係清泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。不過總算學識左職業唔等於光環/為人，同樣applicable to 醫生護士等等。細個諗野係on9啲架喇，大家不如講下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece3cc09afd5fe88c452afd13a381b00e17d8410","tid":179502,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T09:57:07.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"024121bdafcdea004f7a85358fb5d9c8bd04bc06","tid":179502,"uid":13845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T09:58:14.000Z","msg":"女人都係人"},{"pid":"430968a192eafda7b1ee425bf9e6e7553f72a290","tid":179502,"uid":13845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T09:58:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個覺得女人都係人</blockquote>"},{"pid":"0ad9c225de9fa8d34d7fbd0e3d1e9a6149348a2e","tid":179502,"uid":9244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T09:59:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個覺得女人都係人</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n大個發覺男人唔係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8afb957fd4d1fe339d10ad5f63a5df66d200b6","tid":179502,"uid":96129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T09:59:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個覺得女人都係人</blockquote></blockquot